  "3064550": {
    "name": "Twelve Sticks",
    "steam_appid": 3064550,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/dd6b3e72e898f4a53746f839fda36c33.avif?t=1727293003\" width=620 height=140 /></span><br><br>On a summer night, you and your friends gather in the dimly lit garages, where shadows dance as you tell scary stories and play your favorite game, &quot;Twelve Sticks&quot;.<br><br>Each story shared isn’t just a tale—it’s a window into their darkest nightmares.<br><br>We all carry the echoes of childhood nightmares…<br><br>But this night took a turn when a strange girl named Alsu appeared from the shadows. She wanted to join the game, but instead, the boys mocked her and cruelly turned her away.<br><br>With tears streaming down her face, Alsu fled, shouting a chilling warning—she was a hereditary witch.<br><br>And for their cruelty, she vowed to make their worst nightmares come to life.<br><br>The boys scoffed, laughing off her threat, their sneers laced with taunts and obscenities.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/babd86f9d5680afa138a4a146009c977.avif?t=1727293003\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/052c9c1a3cf9dd0644f1ca53db48b465.avif?t=1727293003\" width=620 height=140 /></span><br><br>Hide from the monster, or hunt down children on the map as the monster.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/3ec0b4e32d5361005c018bc008e89cb7.poster.avif?t=1727293003\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/3ec0b4e32d5361005c018bc008e89cb7.webm?t=1727293003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/3ec0b4e32d5361005c018bc008e89cb7.mp4?t=1727293003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The area is infested with terrifying creatures, their presence fills you with anxiety. If you get scared or make too much noise, the monster will easily detect you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/4aefdd076adb18946e8ac93e15c35330.poster.avif?t=1727293003\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/4aefdd076adb18946e8ac93e15c35330.webm?t=1727293003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/4aefdd076adb18946e8ac93e15c35330.mp4?t=1727293003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can temporarily calm your anxiety by holding your breath, but only for a short time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/222da044ae98b5c804658ef556a32eee.poster.avif?t=1727293003\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/222da044ae98b5c804658ef556a32eee.webm?t=1727293003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/222da044ae98b5c804658ef556a32eee.mp4?t=1727293003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Move around on the ground and on garage roofs, but be careful. Falling from a height will take you out of the game for a while, making you an easy target for the monster.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/0f5cd467bec2e6fe33bc0f0a36f75a7c.poster.avif?t=1727293003\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/0f5cd467bec2e6fe33bc0f0a36f75a7c.webm?t=1727293003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/0f5cd467bec2e6fe33bc0f0a36f75a7c.mp4?t=1727293003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>If all players are caught within a single round, the monster is randomly reassigned.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/c4ff02dc22dcbde44611bed742f12fc7.poster.avif?t=1727293003\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/c4ff02dc22dcbde44611bed742f12fc7.webm?t=1727293003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/c4ff02dc22dcbde44611bed742f12fc7.mp4?t=1727293003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The more players participate, the more fun you have. Minimum number of players: 2, maximum: 12.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/7fea2a82d7fa1320ebf8053573f343ef.poster.avif?t=1727293003\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/7fea2a82d7fa1320ebf8053573f343ef.webm?t=1727293003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/7fea2a82d7fa1320ebf8053573f343ef.mp4?t=1727293003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/1df2534db357cf413cb73f019989e17f.avif?t=1727293003\" width=620 height=140 /></span><br><br>The monster earns points for each player caught. When children get scared, they drop fear spheres on the map, which the monster can collect for extra points.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/d77be89948d0953d0d33d3baff039286.poster.avif?t=1727293003\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/d77be89948d0953d0d33d3baff039286.webm?t=1727293003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/d77be89948d0953d0d33d3baff039286.mp4?t=1727293003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Playing as a child character, collect leaves and cones, sell them, and use the points to buy upgrades from the vending machine.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/877b308a274111c9c3477e8dc9c3da4c.poster.avif?t=1727293003\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/877b308a274111c9c3477e8dc9c3da4c.webm?t=1727293003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/877b308a274111c9c3477e8dc9c3da4c.mp4?t=1727293003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Rescue friends caught by the monster and earn bonus points. But be warned—this is extremely dangerous.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/dfc8b9da3455f8f7cdda260b71417731.poster.avif?t=1727293003\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/dfc8b9da3455f8f7cdda260b71417731.webm?t=1727293003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/dfc8b9da3455f8f7cdda260b71417731.mp4?t=1727293003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The player with the most points at the end of the round wins. You can spend them or save them—it's up to you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/c271774453aa9abe9cc8495095dfb1cf.poster.avif?t=1727293003\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/c271774453aa9abe9cc8495095dfb1cf.webm?t=1727293003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/c271774453aa9abe9cc8495095dfb1cf.mp4?t=1727293003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064550/extras/ba24a5b47ec40be5a71d0ed306cbd62f.avif?t=1727293003\" width=620 height=140 /></span><br><br>The game features machine translation into the following languages:<br>- French<br>- German<br>- Spanish<br>- Portuguese (Brazilian)<br>- Chinese (Simplified)<br>- Korean<br>- Polish<br>- Japanese",
